name: Sunshine Gingham
description: The Sunshine Gingham collection is the perfect accessory to any summer day. This bib is a reversible style. There are snaps on each side for easy wearability. One side features yellow and white gingham while the other side is done in delicate, white and yellow striped flannel fabric. The Sunshine Gingham collection is trimmed with eyelet lace.

name: Something Blue
description: The Something Blue bib is feminine without using the traditional "girl" color pink. This bib is a reversible style. There are snaps on each side for easy wearability. One side features delicate blue flowers while the other is done in white terrycloth. Something Blue is trimmed with beautiful lace, an accent that makes it perfect for any little girl.

name: Give a Hoot
description:
Its fun and whimsical. We classify it as a boys bib but it is darling enough to be worn by your little girl as well.

This bib is a reversible style. One side features brown and white gingham with an adorable owl ribbon accent while the other features tan terrycloth. Give a Hoot is trimmed with dark brown piping giving it a crisp clean look.

name: Fancy Floral
description:
It's fun, feminine, and sophisticated. Perfect for any special occasion or for those high maintenance mama's out there with diva babies!

The Fancy Floral bib is a reversible style. One side features a pink and green floral pattern on baby flannel while the other side is cream terrycloth. The bib is trimmed with green balls.

name: Here Fishy Fishy
description: This bib is a reversible style. One side features baby blue flannel with an adorable fish ribbon accent while the other is done in bright yellow terrycloth. Here Fishy Fishy is trimmed with white piping giving it a crisp clean look.
